SUMMARY:Durham Underground Market
DESCRIPTION:The MAKRS Society presents: Durham Underground Market: a market and concert series.\nJoin us for our monthly series featuring new bands every month\, 40+ local vendors\, food trucks\, and more!\nLocation: Durham Central Park\nEvent time: 11am-3pm.\n\nShop from unique vendors. Jam out to awesome music. Grab drinks and food. And make memories with your friends and family!\nMore info on this event: https://makrs.com/durham-underground-market\nInterested in being a vendor? You can apply to any of our events here! https://makrs.com/market-applications
URL:https://durhamcentralpark.org/upcoming-event/durham-underground-market-2/2026-04-26/
LOCATION:Durham Central Park\, 501 Foster Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="MAKRS Society":MAILTO:max@makrs.com
END:VEVENT
