DESCRIPTION:The Durham Farmers’ Market is a community of farmers\, growers and crafters. We are strongly committed to local products: every item you see at the market was produced by the people selling it\, and it all comes from no more than 70 miles away. \nThe Durham Farmers’ Market open Saturdays mornings for local produce\, flowers\, crafts and more! The Wednesday Market is open from 3-6pm Wednesdays\, Mid-April through Mid-October \nIf you’d like more information about this week’s vendor list\, SNAP benefits and map\, visit durhamfarmersmarket.com
URL:https://durhamcentralpark.org/upcoming-event/wednesday-market/2026-05-06/
LOCATION:Durham Central Park\, 501 Foster Street\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Farmers' Market
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://durhamcentralpark.org/content/uploads/HuthPhoto-KAH_6070-1.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Durham Farmers' Market":MAILTO:info@durhamfarmersmarket.com
END:VEVENT
